
Git wrangling
-------------

1. Find the current .git directory (by traversing parent dirs)

2. show prefix (of current dir within repo)

3. parse .git/config

4. find ~/.gitconfig

7. Interpret .git/objects/pack/*.pack files:

0000000: 5041 434b 0000 0002 0000 1745 9915 789c  PACK.......E..x.

objects/pack/pack-03dd807efaffb1084f2a314ee633591a21f9166e.pack: Git
pack, version 2, 5957 objects

(0x1745 = 5957)

Haskell cruft
-------------

Use Data.Binary for reading

Use a left-fold enumerator for following branch histories
